<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>SJ SHOP</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="container hero-shell">
                <div class="hero-copy">
                    <div class="hero-badge">AI PPT MATCHING</div>
                    <h1 class="hero-title">
                        <span class="hero-title-primary">원하는 PPT를 말해보세요.</span>
                        <span class="hero-title-accent">AI가 템플릿을 추천해드려요</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p class="hero-desc">분위기, 목적, 업종, 사용 장면만 설명하면 어울리는 PPT를 빠르게 찾아드립니다.</p>
                </div>

                <form id="main-ppt-search-form" class="hero-search-panel" action="/ppt-lab-page" method="get">
                    <label for="main-ppt-search" class="hero-search-label">어떤 PPT가 필요한지 자유롭게 입력해보세요</label>

                    <div class="hero-search-body">
                        <span class="hero-search-attach" aria-hidden="true">✦</span>
                        <input
                            type="text"
                            id="main-ppt-search"
                            name="q"
                            class="hero-search-input"
                            placeholder="예: 차분한 톤의 기업 소개서, 교육용 발표 자료, 감성적인 포트폴리오"
                            autocomplete="off"
                        />
                        <button type="submit" class="hero-search-submit" aria-label="AI 추천 받기">
                            <span>↗</span>
                        </button>
                    </div>

                    <div class="hero-actions">
                        <a href="/ppt-lab-page?q=브랜드 소개서" class="hero-chip-link">브랜드 소개서</a>
                        <a href="/ppt-lab-page?q=회사 소개" class="hero-chip-link">회사 소개</a>
                        <a href="/ppt-lab-page?q=강의 발표" class="hero-chip-link">강의 발표</a>
                        <a href="/ppt-lab-page?q=이벤트 기획안" class="hero-chip-link">이벤트 기획안</a>
                        <a href="/ppt-lab-page?q=교육 자료" class="hero-chip-link">교육 자료</a>
                        <a href="/products-page" class="hero-chip-link hero-chip-link-muted">상품리스트 보기</a>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="home-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-head">
                    <h2 class="section-title">추천 템플릿</h2>
                    <a href="/products-page" class="section-link">전체 보기</a>
                </div>

                <div class="home-product-grid" id="featured-products-grid">
                    <p class="empty-message">추천 템플릿을 불러오는 중입니다.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/common.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
